  <section>
    <h2>Public Surfaces</h2>

    <p>
      Meta-Writing Ecology can be entered through fiction, system documents,
      corpus-facing materials, and public publication records. These surfaces do
      not replace the system architecture. They provide different points of
      access to the same recursive language ecology.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
